Author: poopybuttholeboy
Text: Aww honey, I feel you sister, I feel like I’m sitting in the exact same position as you, I know I need to start being really honest with everyone around me about my thoughts and anxieties around food, I’m not able to fight them off but maybe making others aware of them is the first step in getting them under control maybe saying them out loud will weaken them some how?! It’s the only way out I can see.
